      "value": "<p>Whenever a weapon attack (not including siege weapons, or other massive weapons) misses a creature benefiting from your active defense, you may choose a new target for the attack within its original range (for ranged attacks) or reach (for melee attacks) as a free action that can be taken even when it&#8217;s not your turn, comparing the original attack roll, with a -2 penalty, to the new target&#8217;s AC and resolving the attack as normal on a successful hit.</p>\n",
